  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The program is a continuation of Adinas ongoing work(since 2010)  for disabled children (CWD), imlpemented in Northern Uganda in partnership with their local partner AFU (Adina Foundation Uganda). The  project focuses on localizing, assessment, rehabilitation and follow-up of CWDs in addition to outreach work with their families and communities. LRC incorporates both
institutionalized rehabilitation (IR) (with the implementation of corrective surgeries) and community-based rehabilitation (CBR).</narrative>
  </description>
